    "description": "Are you a skilled Supply Chain Manager looking for your next big career move? Safexpress Ventures Solutions in Tiruchirappalli offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Safexpress Ventures Solutions:\nSafexpress Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Safexpress Ventures Solutions!",
